How do you burn this? I have now changed the file from IMG to ISO, just typed .iso after the file name, and then it should work right? I use Nero burning rom and it fails constantely and if I burn it like the img file it is then my dvd player dosnt play it.

Help!

Open Nero Burning Rom under Data sub-menu
Cancel on guides coming up
Go to Recorder menu -> Burn image
Choose any image file to burn (img, iso, bin/cue etc)
Choose Write
Choose Finalize (no further writing)
Choose Lower speed if you have time
Choose Disc-at-once write method
Click Burn

Or even better, use a virtual cd/dvd tool to mount the img, iso, bin/cue images instead of wasting power and plastic resources on burning to a disc you probably only will use 1-4 times. Just as fun, but better and faster in case you don't need the standalone dvd-player :)
